&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Given:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Eight girls A, B, C, D, E, F, G and&amp;nbsp;H&amp;nbsp;are sitting around a circular table facing towards the centre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;A is second to the left of D.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;D is third to the left of E.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/26/03/IMG-2115-VISHAL-1-A.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 191px; width: 189px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3) G is not the immediate neighbour of&amp;nbsp;E.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;4)&amp;nbsp;C is third to the right of G.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;5) B&amp;nbsp;is second to the right of&amp;nbsp;G.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/26/03/IMG-2115-VISHAL-2.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 203px; height: 191px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;6)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;H&amp;nbsp;is third to the right of&amp;nbsp;B.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;After positioning H only one position is left which will be occupied by the only girl left i.e F.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/26/03/IMG-2115-VISHAL-1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 218px; height: 221px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Thus, according to the final arrangement A&amp;nbsp;is sitting on the immediate left of&amp;nbsp;G.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 4&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;दिया गया है:&lt;/span&gt; आठ लड़कियाँ A, B, C, D, E, F, G और H एक गोल मेज के चारों ओर केंद्र के सम्मुख बैठी हैं।&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1) A, D के बायें&amp;nbsp;से दूसरी है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2) &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;D, E के बायें&amp;nbsp;से तीसरी है।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/26/03/IMG-2115-VISHAL-1-A.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); height: 191px; width: 189px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3) G, E की तत्काल पड़ोसी नहीं है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;4) C, G के दायें&amp;nbsp;से तीसरी है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;5) B, G के दायें&amp;nbsp;से दूसरी है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/26/03/IMG-2115-VISHAL-2.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 203px; height: 191px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;6) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;H, B के दायें&amp;nbsp;से तीसरी है। &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;H को रखने के बाद केवल एक स्थान बचा है जिस पर शेष लड़की अर्थात&amp;nbsp;F स्थापित होगी।&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/26/03/IMG-2115-VISHAL-1.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 218px; height: 221px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;इस प्रकार, अंतिम व्यवस्था के अनुसार A, G के तत्काल बायें&amp;nbsp;बैठी है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;इसलिए,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;सही उत्तर&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;विकल्प 4&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/br%20testbook%20%281%29.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 243px; height: 356px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;A is the spouse of B who has no female child.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2) C is the brother of D and E who is the son of B.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/F3_Vinanti_State%20Govt._14.12.22_D32.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 238px; height: 96px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3)&amp;nbsp;A is not the mother of D.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/F3_Vinanti_State%20Govt._14.12.22_D33.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 251px; height: 109px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, D is the son of B.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/br%20testbook%20%281%29.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 243px; height: 356px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;दिया गया है:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1) A, B का जीवनसाथी है जिसकी कोई लड़की नहीं है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2) C, D और E का भाई है जो B का पुत्र है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/F3_Vinanti_State%20Govt._14.12.22_D32.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 238px; height: 96px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3) A, D की &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;माँ&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;नहीं है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/F3_Vinanti_State%20Govt._14.12.22_D33.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 251px; height: 109px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;अतः D, B का पुत्र है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;अतः, सही उत्तर &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;विकल्प 1&amp;quot; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;है।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6800c48003e0556726df16e3.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Option 1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;IGECA : NLJHF&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6800c48103e0556726df16e4.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-36.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 152px; height: 76px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 2)&amp;nbsp;YWUSQ : DBZXV&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6800c48103e0556726df16e5.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-37.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 152px; height: 77px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 3)&amp;nbsp;HFDBZ : MKIGE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6800c48203e0556726df16e6.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-38.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 152px; height: 76px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 4)&amp;nbsp;PRTVX : UWYAC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6800c48203e0556726df16e7.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-39.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 152px; height: 76px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here, doesn&amp;#39;t follow the pattern.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 4&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6800c48003e0556726df16e3.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;यहाँ अनुसरित तर्क निम्न है:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;विकल्प 1) &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;IGECA : NLJHF&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-36.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 152px; height: 76px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;विकल्प 2) YWUSQ : DBZXV&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-37.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 152px; height: 77px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;विकल्प 3) HFDBZ : MKIGE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-38.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 152px; height: 76px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;विकल्प 4) PRTVX : UWYAC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/09/IMG-1277-Arpit-39.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 152px; height: 76px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;यहाँ, पैटर्न का अनुसरण नहीं&amp;nbsp;होता है।&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;इसलिए, सही उत्तर &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;विकल्प 4&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; है।&lt;/p&gt;

